e"></span><br><span class="line">千里之外不离开</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">把所有的春天</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">都揉进了一个清晨</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">把所有停不下的言语变成秘密</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">关上了门</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">莫名的情愫啊请问</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">谁来将它带走呢</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">只好把岁月化成歌</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">留在山河</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

